324
00:23:48,218 --> 00:23:49,052
What?

325
00:23:49,761 --> 00:23:51,722
That you're different from others.

326
00:23:52,723 --> 00:23:53,724
I forgot that for a while.

327
00:23:58,270 --> 00:23:59,313
I must've unknowingly

328
