504
00:37:18,569 --> 00:37:19,779
"He told us not to call her."

505
00:37:24,117 --> 00:37:26,494
Thank you! Thank you so much.

506
00:37:27,245 --> 00:37:28,663
Thank you.

507
00:37:35,169 --> 00:37:36,045
My gosh.

